To enable the numbered page navigation style, open your `pages.php` file then find code that looks like one of the examples below:

~~~ .html
<nav><?= $pager; ?></nav>
~~~

~~~ .php
<?= self::pager(); ?>
~~~

Replace with this:

~~~ .php
<?= self::pager('step'); ?>
~~~

### Types

Type | Description
---- | -----------
`step` | Numbered page navigation.
`title` | Add page title to the next and previous link.
